title: Chile Food Inflation
description: Cost of food in Chile increased 21.93 percent in September of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Food Inflation in Chile averaged 5.63 percent from 2014 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 21.93 percent in September of 2022 and a record low of -0.40 percent in September of 2017. This page provides - Chile Food Inflation - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Institute of Statistics, Chile
